  <p class="clue">

    Three glimpses of art, scattered in time,
    Each holds a <span class="highlight">name</span>, a clue in its prime.

    One shows a number, not too small,
    The second, a melody—a love-filled call.
    The last, where coins and ledgers reside,
    Count the meaning—let fate be your guide.

    Fill the blanks, vowels in <span class="highlight">hue</span>,
    A <span class="highlight">phrase</span> to mark our love so true.
    The end is near, just one thing—
    Find the titles, and let them sing.
  </p>
  
